; Project-local npm config.
; Pin the registry to the official public npm registry so that
; `package-lock.json` URLs and CI installs never leak a contributor's
; private/Nexus/Artifactory configuration from `~/.npmrc`.
; If you need a private mirror for *your* machine, set it in `~/.npmrc`
; only for unscoped fetches — this file will still win for this project.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
